  "texts": [
    "The Federal Aviation Administration (FAA) of the United States predicts that demand for commercial UAV installation will quadruple by 2023 (Administration, 2019).",
    "Due to the enormous potential of UAVs, several countries are devoting significant financial resources to their broad commercial deployment.",
    "UAV-assisted networks continue to face several difficulties despite the growing potential and many uses of UAVs.",
    "These difficulties include concerns with the planning of routes, privacy concerns, hurdle handling, energy efficiency, and optimizing for minimal delays (Ateya et al., 2019).",
    "These problems must be dealt with adequately if we are to harness the potential offered by UAVs."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "The Federal Aviation Administration (FAA) of the United States predicts that demand for commercial UAV installation will quadruple by 2023 (Administration, 2019).",
    "These difficulties include concerns with the planning of routes, privacy concerns, hurdle handling, energy efficiency, and optimizing for minimal delays (Ateya et al., 2019)."
  ]
